query:
/*+ NoMergeJoin(ci mk t mi) NoMergeJoin(ci mi mk t mc) */ select count(*)
from movie_keyword AS mk
inner join title AS t
on t.id = mk.movie_id AND mk.keyword_id = 7084 AND t.production_year > 2000 AND t.production_year < 2010
inner join cast_info AS ci
on t.id = ci.movie_id AND ci.role_id = 2
inner join movie_info AS mi
on t.id = mi.movie_id AND mi.info_type_id = 16
inner join movie_companies AS mc
on t.id = mc.movie_id;
